me1200PortConfigEntry.description: Each port interface has a set of parameters

me1200PortConfigShutdown.name: me1200PortConfigShutdown
me1200PortConfigShutdown.description: Controls whether interface is shutdown or powered up. Set to TRUE in order to power down the interface.

me1200PortConfigDuplex.name: me1200PortConfigDuplex
me1200PortConfigDuplex.description: Controls the port duplex. For setting duplex auto-negotiation it is require that the port speed is set in auto-negotiation mode first. It is only possible to set duplex to half duplex if the port speed is either set to 10Mbit or 100Mbit forced speed.

me1200PortConfigFC.name: me1200PortConfigFC
me1200PortConfigFC.description: Controls the port flow control mode.

me1200PortConfigMTU.name: me1200PortConfigMTU
me1200PortConfigMTU.description: Controls the port's Maximum Transmission Unit.

me1200PortConfigExcessiveRestart.name: me1200PortConfigExcessiveRestart
me1200PortConfigExcessiveRestart.description: TRUE to restart half-duplex back-off algorithm after 16 collisions. FALSE to discard frame after 16 collisions
